data.description: Step into your private oasis on a little over 3 acres of serene countryside with this splendid 4-bedroom, 2-bath home. Every inch of this abode has been adorned with BRAND-NEW carpet, giving it a fresh, inviting feel. A detached 2-car garage, a rare gem in the market, offers ample space for storage or your personal workshop. The primary bedroom, generously designed, comes with an additional sitting room, perfect for crafting a cozy reading corner or a productive home office. Further notable features of this property include a private well, a recently installed roof, and a secure, fenced backyard - an ideal haven for your beloved pets. Discover a lifestyle that seamlessly blends space, practicality, and the natural beauty of the surroundings. This home has so much more to offer! Don't miss your opportunity to see it today!
